# UI styling

`lang`/`dir` on **root layout only** — defaults from `src/lib/app-locale.ts`. **Logical Tailwind** (`me`/`ms`, `start`/`end`, …). **shadcn** from `src/components/ui` — default variants; compose before custom markup. **Never hand-edit `src/components/ui/*`** for app behavior or fixes — wrap/extend in `src/app/**` or `src/components/` (outside `ui/`); regen primitives with shadcn CLI. Reuse existing UI up the tree; hoist shared pieces to the highest relevant scope (segment `components/` → `src/components/`). Base UI: `render={<Link … />}`, not `asChild`. **`Button` / `TabsTrigger` + `Link`:** `nativeButton={false}` at call sites in app code.

English; dashboard chrome copy in `dashboard-nav-labels.ts` — no i18n unless user asks.

**Dashboard tables:** long DB-backed text → `truncate` + field-level `max-w-*` on the text node; no global table layout helpers — [ui-design.md § Dashboard tables](docs/agents/ui-design.md#dashboard-tables-variable-db-text).

